milestones.description: This is the lowest match aggregate (406) involving teams Zimbabwe & Ireland in ODIs

stories.title: Zimbabwe edge low-scoring thriller
stories.subTitle: Zimbabwe v Ireland, 1st ODI, Harare
stories.summary: Ed Rainsford was Zimbabwe's hero as they squeaked home with a last-ball, two-wicket win in the first one-day international at Harare Sports Club

image.caption: Ed Rainsford celebrates after hitting the winning runs
image.longCaption: Ed Rainsford celebrates after hitting the winning runs, Zimbabwe v Ireland, 1st ODI, Harare, September 26, 2010
